        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/c/fbc32d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2020-10-31T18:35:00.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I hope William Kelley sees this thread, but if anyone can answer, I would appreciate it. I see listings for Domaine Daniel Barraud, Domaine Daniel et Julien Barraud and Domaine Daniel et Martine Barraud, all with different labels, but they all appear to be one family. Is there a difference in the bottlings? Even on one of the importers websites, it listed Daniel et Martine Barraud as the producer, while the picture of the label showed \u201cDomaine Barraud.\u201d It\u2019s very confusing.</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
