        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/c/fbc32d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2020-10-31T18:45:58.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thanks, William. On the WA website, it lists the wines you reviewed under the name \u201cDaniel et Julien Barraud.\u201d If I see a different label for the equivalent wine (i.e., \u201cPouilly-Fuisse En France\u201d), it should be the same wine as the one you reviewed?</p>",
