      {
        "id": 3015725,
        "name": "Chris_Rickey",
        "username": "crickey",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/c/fbc32d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2020-10-31T19:25:49.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I don\u2019t think it is out-of-date. I see pictures with \u201cDaniel et Julien Barraud\u201d on the label of 2017 wines. It\u2019s just that I also see pictures with other labels on what appears to be the same wine. I was wondering if the naming convention might relate to different importers, but even one importer\u2019s website listed one name and the picture of the label showed another. Maybe you can ask the next time you drink with Daniel, Martine and/or Julien. <img src=\"/images/emoji/unicode/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
