        "created_at": "2020-11-03T14:29:47.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Fwiw, I checked a bottle in inventory, the '17 St Veran Pommards, and it says Domaine Barraud.<br>\nTo your point, Chris, I don\u2019t believe different labels are different wines.<br>\nSame wine.</p>",
